videos.description: Jordan Davis throws a ball to only where Devin Scott can catch it for a 28-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Louisiana gets on the board 50 seconds into the game

videos.description: Jordan Davis calls his own number on the first play of the game for a 47-yard gain.
videos.headline: Louisiana's Davis breaks free for 47 yards

videos.description: Taylor Lamb flips a pass over the middle to Ike Lewis, who runs to the outside and sprints down the sidelines for a 48-yard catch.
videos.headline: Appalachian State's Lewis turns on jets for 48-yard catch-and-run

videos.description: Taylor Lamb fakes the handoff and escapes for a 29-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Appalachian State's Lamb ties game with TD run

videos.description: Taylor Lamb finds an open Thomas Hennigan, who beats one defender for an easy 33-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Appalachian State's Hennigan eludes defender for TD
